title: After Catalan Independence, it's time for London Independence - See why.......
description:
In the tax year 2015-16 every Londoner provided £3,070 more in tax revenues than they received in public spending
* London’s economy generates a £26.5bn tax surplus (that is £500 million every week) 
* London economy subsidises rest of UK,
* London generates 30% of UK taxes, the Capital responsible for more tax than next 37 cities combined
ONS figures show.
